            "mentions": [
                {
                    "quoted_text": "Our analysis revealed that the majority (78.8%) of the somatic variants detected was also found in PB. However, three deleterious mutations (BRCA1: c.986del, BRCA2: C.3187C>T, BRCA2: c.5351del) as well as two VUS (BRCA1: c.**4046 C>G**, RAD51D: c.298C>T) were not present in PB. Because of the lack of the corresponding PB sample, for two somatic variants (BRCA1: c.5216-1G>A, BRIP1: c.1315C>T) the germline testing was not possible.",
